== Outline ==

 * http://www.patentdefenceunion.org/
 * founded by [http://swpat.ffii.org/patents/effects/allvoice/ Allvoice] CEO John Mitchell, a software service company that turned to patents as its center of activity
 * calling for regulations that facilitate patent enforcement by small companies, including Patent Insurance
